1694378754\" width=491 height=30 /></span><br><strong> </strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 无需加载屏幕即可无缝探索 7 个不同的相互关联的区域<br></li><li> 使用麦克风解决难题<br></li><li> 管理您的库存并选择要采取的路径<br></li><li> 武器库可帮助您控制局势<br></li><li> 多样化的角色阵容，将帮助您揭开真相</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444580/extras/45c6fb5e15584ca533aa727ecb9876ee.poster.avif?t=1694378754\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444580/extras/45c6fb5e15584ca533aa727ecb9876ee.webm?t=1694378754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444580/extras/45c6fb5e15584ca533aa727ecb9876ee.mp4?t=1694378754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
